                            <p>We generate a secure link and secret key that you can share with the recipient.</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="step">
                            <div class="step-number">4</div>
                            <h3>Recipient Accesses File</h3>
                            <p>The recipient uses the link and password (if set) to download the file within 3 days.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
