                    <div class="faq-list">
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <div class="faq-question">
                                <span>What types of files can I share with SafeDrop?</span>
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <p>SafeDrop supports all common file types including images (JPG, PNG, GIF), documents (PDF, DOCX, XLSX, PPTX), audio files (MP3, WAV), video files (MP4, MOV), and more. The maximum file size is 2GB/file for premium users and 50MB/file for free users.</p>
                            </div>
