                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <div class="faq-question">
                                <span>How secure is SafeDrop?</span>
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <p>SafeDrop uses industry-standard AES-256 encryption for all files during transfer and storage. Files are automatically deleted after 3 days, and you can add an additional layer of security with password protection. We don't scan or access your files' contents.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="faq-item">
